[
  {
    "text": "President Trump is touting",
    "start": 0.033,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "what could be",
    "start": 1.301,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "a financial windfall",
    "start": 2.302,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "for the United States.",
    "start": 3.403,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "But at whose expense",
    "start": 4.371,
    "duration": 1.801
  },
  {
    "text": "is it American consumers?",
    "start": 6.172,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "It's based on Trump's new",
    "start": 7.941,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "tariff rates",
    "start": 9.075,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "for various countries.",
    "start": 9.843,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "The Congressional Budget Office",
    "start": 10.844,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "updated its projections",
    "start": 12.012,
    "duration": 1.067
  },
  {
    "text": "and now estimates that Trump's",
    "start": 13.079,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "tariffs could reduce the U.S.",
    "start": 14.481,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "deficit by a whopping",
    "start": 15.915,
    "duration": 1.469
  },
  {
    "text": "$4 trillion",
    "start": 17.384,
    "duration": 2.836
  },
  {
    "text": "over the next ten years.",
    "start": 20.22,
    "duration": 1.067
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's bring in Justin Wolfers.",
    "start": 21.287,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "He's a professor of economics",
    "start": 22.489,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "and public policy",
    "start": 23.59,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "at the University of Michigan.",
    "start": 24.858,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "So, first of all,",
    "start": 26.793,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "what do you think",
    "start": 28.395,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "are the chances",
    "start": 28.895,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "that the tariffs",
    "start": 29.496,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "will actually",
    "start": 30.063,
    "duration": 0.434
  },
  {
    "text": "last through 2035,",
    "start": 30.497,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "which the CBO is basing",
    "start": 32.799,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "its estimates on.",
    "start": 34.2,
    "duration": 2.469
  },
  {
    "text": "And close to? No chance.",
    "start": 36.669,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's",
    "start": 37.971,
    "duration": 0.3
  },
  {
    "text": "one of the biggest problems,",
    "start": 38.271,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "which is",
    "start": 39.305,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "the whole idea of tariffs.",
    "start": 40.34,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "As you provide an incentive",
    "start": 42.175,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "for people to set up shop at,",
    "start": 43.176,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "the tariffs are going to change",
    "start": 44.644,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "before the shop gets set up.",
    "start": 45.745,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "And as a result, I'm not sure",
    "start": 47.18,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "we're going to get much action",
    "start": 48.548,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "out of this.",
    "start": 49.582,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "So then the big question",
    "start": 50.55,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "about this $4 trillion is",
    "start": 51.684,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "where is this $4",
    "start": 53.319,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "trillion coming from?",
    "start": 54.287,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Is it coming from",
    "start": 55.155,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "foreign governments?",
    "start": 55.789,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Is it coming from",
    "start": 56.589,
    "duration": 0.568
  },
  {
    "text": "foreign companies",
    "start": 57.157,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "for months here in the lead?",
    "start": 58.124,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "We've been talking",
    "start": 59.459,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "to small business leaders",
    "start": 60.026,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "about how the tariffs",
    "start": 60.994,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "are affecting them.",
    "start": 61.828,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Most of them say",
    "start": 62.829,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "that they are currently",
    "start": 63.63,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "eating the tariffs,",
    "start": 64.531,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "but eventually are going",
    "start": 65.799,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "to have to pass on the cost",
    "start": 66.766,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "to their consumers.",
    "start": 68.601,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "So I wonder in this projection,",
    "start": 69.502,
    "duration": 1.869
  },
  {
    "text": "who pays this $4 trillion?",
    "start": 71.371,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "Is it mostly",
    "start": 73.306,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "American consumers?",
    "start": 73.94,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 76.709,
    "duration": 0.201
  },
  {
    "text": "Jake,I want to come",
    "start": 76.91,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "back to something",
    "start": 78.078,
    "duration": 0.533
  },
  {
    "text": "you said in the lead.",
    "start": 78.611,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "You said this windfall",
    "start": 79.746,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "for the American budget.",
    "start": 81.247,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not a windfall.",
    "start": 82.582,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a tax.",
    "start": 83.716,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "And when you charge people",
    "start": 85.051,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "a tax,",
    "start": 86.086,
    "duration": 0.633
  },
  {
    "text": "the government gets revenue.",
    "start": 86.719,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "It's as simple as that.",
    "start": 87.72,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "In this case,",
    "start": 89.389,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "here's how it works.",
    "start": 90.123,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "If Best Buy,",
    "start": 91.558,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "if if Best Buy brings",
    "start": 92.325,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "in a washing machine,",
    "start": 93.526,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "say, from Korea,",
    "start": 94.661,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "that washing",
    "start": 96.596,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "machine gets shipped to America",
    "start": 97.33,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "and it sits in the port",
    "start": 98.531,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "in customs,",
    "start": 99.999,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "and it can't get out of customs",
    "start": 101.034,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "until BestBuy writes",
    "start": 102.836,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "a check for the tariff.",
    "start": 103.97,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "So at the first level,",
    "start": 105.972,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Best Buy,",
    "start": 106.973,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "an American company,",
    "start": 107.507,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "is paying the tariff.",
    "start": 108.274,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "But we economists",
    "start": 109.843,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "like to look at",
    "start": 110.677,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "a little hotter.",
    "start": 111.144,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "Everything's connected",
    "start": 111.678,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "to everything else.",
    "start": 112.345,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "So there are some other things",
    "start": 113.613,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "that could happen.",
    "start": 114.781,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, Samsung could decide",
    "start": 116.116,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "what they want to do",
    "start": 117.484,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "is keep their market share,",
    "start": 118.118,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "which means they'd have to",
    "start": 119.252,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "cut the price",
    "start": 120.253,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "they're selling that",
    "start": 121.054,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "washing machine at.",
    "start": 121.654,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "But there's a price index",
    "start": 123.156,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "called the import price index.",
    "start": 124.457,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "And it measures the price",
    "start": 126.526,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "of our imports.",
    "start": 128.194,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Not surprising",
    "start": 129.062,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "that has not fallen a penny.",
    "start": 130.563,
    "duration": 2.269
  },
  {
    "text": "What that means",
    "start": 132.832,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "is that Trump's promise",
    "start": 134.2,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "that foreign companies",
    "start": 135.969,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "would pay this tax",
    "start": 137.103,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "turned out to be false.",
    "start": 138.538,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "At the moment,",
    "start": 140.64,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "Best Buy's paying the tax.",
    "start": 141.774,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "But probably",
    "start": 143.843,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "what's starting to happen.",
    "start": 144.611,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "What has started to happen?",
    "start": 145.578,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "A few places",
    "start": 146.546,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "and will happen more over",
    "start": 147.347,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "the next few months is Best",
    "start": 148.381,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "Buy will discover",
    "start": 149.949,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "that its costs are going up,",
    "start": 150.65,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "and then it's",
    "start": 152.252,
    "duration": 0.433
  },
  {
    "text": "going to jack up the price.",
    "start": 152.685,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "But either way,",
    "start": 154.187,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "the cost is being borne",
    "start": 154.687,
    "duration": 0.835
  },
  {
    "text": "by Americans right",
    "start": 155.522,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "now, by Best Buy",
    "start": 156.389,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "and therefore",
    "start": 157.257,
    "duration": 0.367
  },
  {
    "text": "by my 401K",
    "start": 157.624,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "which is invested in that.",
    "start": 158.591,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "Later on",
    "start": 161.094,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "they'll jack up the price",
    "start": 161.961,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "and it'll be American",
    "start": 163.096,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "consumers.",
    "start": 163.863,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "Simple point here.",
    "start": 164.497,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a tax on Americans",
    "start": 165.365,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "being paid by Americans. Yeah.",
    "start": 166.599,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "Just to be clear,",
    "start": 168.301,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "when I said windfall,",
    "start": 169.002,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "I was saying that's what",
    "start": 169.802,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "President Trump",
    "start": 170.503,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "how President Trump",
    "start": 171.204,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "is describing this.",
    "start": 172.105,
    "duration": 2.269
  },
  {
    "text": "so what to do with the $4",
    "start": 174.374,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "trillion",
    "start": 176.142,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "coming from the tariffs?",
    "start": 176.709,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "Trump",
    "start": 177.677,
    "duration": 0.267
  },
  {
    "text": "one said he was considering",
    "start": 177.944,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "a kind of tariff",
    "start": 178.978,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "rebate check",
    "start": 180.046,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "for American consumers.",
    "start": 180.947,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's",
    "start": 182.549,
    "duration": 0.266
  },
  {
    "text": "what the Treasury",
    "start": 182.815,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "secretary said about that.",
    "start": 183.349,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "I think at a point",
    "start": 184.651,
    "duration": 1.801
  },
  {
    "text": "we're going to be able",
    "start": 186.452,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "to do it.",
    "start": 187.253,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "But President",
    "start": 187.921,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "Trump and I are laser",
    "start": 189.022,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "focused on paying down",
    "start": 190.49,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "the debt. What do you think?",
    "start": 191.925,
    "duration": 1.534
  },
  {
    "text": "I think he's",
    "start": 195.662,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "exactly right,",
    "start": 196.229,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "that it would be crazy",
    "start": 197.063,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "for there to be a rebate check.",
    "start": 198.431,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "By the way,",
    "start": 199.465,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "Jake,",
    "start": 199.966,
    "duration": 0.367
  },
  {
    "text": "do you remember",
    "start": 200.333,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "just a few months ago,",
    "start": 200.9,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "we were being told",
    "start": 201.801,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "that there would be",
    "start": 202.569,
    "duration": 0.533
  },
  {
    "text": "so many trillions",
    "start": 203.102,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "of dollars saved by dollars,",
    "start": 204.003,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "we'd all be getting",
    "start": 205.371,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "rebate checks.",
    "start": 205.972,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "And I went all over",
    "start": 207.073,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "TV having arguments with people",
    "start": 207.774,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "saying how big",
    "start": 209.642,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "with the rebate check be.",
    "start": 210.276,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "And it turns out Doge",
    "start": 211.911,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "never saved anything.",
    "start": 212.912,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "In this case,",
    "start": 214.48,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "the Republicans just passed",
    "start": 215.148,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "a budget.",
    "start": 216.249,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "Their budget took an already",
    "start": 216.716,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "existing budget deficit",
    "start": 217.984,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "and made it worse.",
    "start": 219.619,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's not talk in trillions.",
    "start": 221.154,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "What this is is basically 400",
    "start": 222.355,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "billion per year",
    "start": 224.29,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "over ten years.",
    "start": 225.491,
    "duration": 0.835
  },
  {
    "text": "That's easy",
    "start": 226.326,
    "duration": 0.433
  },
  {
    "text": "way to think about it.",
    "start": 226.759,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "And basically",
    "start": 228.361,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "they've already spent that.",
    "start": 229.162,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "They've spent that",
    "start": 229.996,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "giving tax cuts to rich people.",
    "start": 230.697,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "So what does this mean.",
    "start": 232.165,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "It means overall",
    "start": 233.132,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "what we've done is",
    "start": 234.267,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "we've swapped one",
    "start": 234.901,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "set of taxes for another.",
    "start": 235.635,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "It used to be",
    "start": 237.704,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "we had high income taxes on",
    "start": 238.338,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "rich people.",
    "start": 239.606,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "We've gotten rid of that.",
    "start": 240.807,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "And to fill the budget hall",
    "start": 242.208,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "we're now",
    "start": 243.409,
    "duration": 0.401
  },
  {
    "text": "putting tariffs on now.",
    "start": 243.81,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Tariffs are paid by everyone.",
    "start": 245.645,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "There are sales",
    "start": 247.013,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "tax effectively.",
    "start": 247.747,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "And so that means",
    "start": 249.015,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "we've shifted taxes",
    "start": 249.916,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "from the rich",
    "start": 251.084,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "to the working middle class.",
    "start": 252.952,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Because all of us",
    "start": 254.12,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "buy imported stuff.",
    "start": 254.854,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "And therefore all of us",
    "start": 255.755,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "are paying these tariffs.",
    "start": 256.556,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Justin Wolfers,",
    "start": 258.224,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "University of Michigan.",
    "start": 259.325,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you so much.",
    "start": 260.293,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Good to see you, sir.",
    "start": 260.96,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Pleasure, man.",
    "start": 263.162,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "Fontana Forni,",
    "start": 264.397,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "USA is a business",
    "start": 265.832,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "that imports high",
    "start": 267.166,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "end outdoor pizza",
    "start": 268.101,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "ovens",
    "start": 269.702,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "directly",
    "start": 270.503,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "from the family",
    "start": 271.738,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "owned manufacturer in Italy.",
    "start": 272.639,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "It's been in operation",
    "start": 275.308,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "since 1978. The U.S.",
    "start": 276.175,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "distributor works",
    "start": 277.71,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "in close collaboration",
    "start": 278.411,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "with the Fontana family",
    "start": 279.779,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "to bring their designs",
    "start": 281.114,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "exclusively to North America.",
    "start": 282.115,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "And CEO",
    "start": 283.349,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "Jeremy Lande joins me now.",
    "start": 284.183,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "Jeremy, thanks for joining us.",
    "start": 285.451,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "So your business relies",
    "start": 286.552,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "on an imported imported product",
    "start": 288.921,
    "duration": 2.47
  },
  {
    "text": "that you can only get",
    "start": 291.391,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "from Italy.",
    "start": 292.225,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "How have the tariffs",
    "start": 293.493,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "changed things for you?",
    "start": 294.661,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah. Hi, Jake.",
    "start": 297.73,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks.",
    "start": 298.531,
    "duration": 0.367
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for having me on.",
    "start": 298.898,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "The tariffs have impacted us",
    "start": 299.899,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "in a couple of different ways.",
    "start": 301.734,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "The first one is",
    "start": 303.67,
    "duration": 1.067
  },
  {
    "text": "is just being able",
    "start": 304.737,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "to figure out",
    "start": 305.938,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "how to navigate them.",
    "start": 306.572,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "What most people",
    "start": 308.241,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "don't understand",
    "start": 308.908,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "is there's actually two tariffs",
    "start": 309.475,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "on our products.",
    "start": 311.311,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "The first one is",
    "start": 312.145,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "just the standard 15%",
    "start": 312.745,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "EU tariff.",
    "start": 314.681,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "But then we have",
    "start": 315.381,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "a second tariff,",
    "start": 315.882,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "which is the steel tariff",
    "start": 317.016,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "which is",
    "start": 318.618,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "50% of the cost of the steel.",
    "start": 319.986,
    "duration": 2.469
  },
  {
    "text": "So to give some perspective,",
    "start": 322.455,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "in June",
    "start": 324.757,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "I had two ocean",
    "start": 325.658,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "containers come in",
    "start": 326.859,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "and they were",
    "start": 328.961,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "taxed at over 80%.",
    "start": 329.629,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "And so we paid our 80%",
    "start": 331.931,
    "duration": 2.436
  },
  {
    "text": "tariff on on these",
    "start": 334.367,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "ocean containers",
    "start": 336.469,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "that came in",
    "start": 337.203,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "and later found out that",
    "start": 338.304,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "that isn't exactly",
    "start": 339.806,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "what the situation is working",
    "start": 340.84,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "with our customs brokers,",
    "start": 342.542,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "they're not even exactly sure",
    "start": 343.71,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "what the procedures are.",
    "start": 345.178,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "So not only does it",
    "start": 346.412,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "tie up cash,",
    "start": 347.747,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "it's just it's hard to plan",
    "start": 349.082,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "and it constantly",
    "start": 350.95,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "has us rethinking",
    "start": 352.685,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "inventory levels.",
    "start": 353.686,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "80% tax or tariff is a lot.",
    "start": 354.754,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "How are you",
    "start": 358.057,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "weathering the costs?",
    "start": 358.991,
    "duration": 1.102
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you have to raise prices?",
    "start": 360.093,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "So, it looks as if",
    "start": 363.596,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "because the landscape",
    "start": 365.798,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "is only always changing,",
    "start": 366.833,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "that we're not going to have",
    "start": 367.967,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "an 80% tariff",
    "start": 369.001,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "at this point in time.",
    "start": 370.036,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "But honestly,",
    "start": 371.371,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "we're not exactly sure",
    "start": 372.038,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "where it's going to land.",
    "start": 373.439,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "But yeah, we've",
    "start": 374.44,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "we've had to raise prices.",
    "start": 375.808,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "August 1st",
    "start": 377.844,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "was our first price",
    "start": 378.544,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "increase in in years.",
    "start": 379.846,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's something",
    "start": 381.914,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "that we absolutely",
    "start": 382.849,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "don't take lightly.",
    "start": 383.983,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "We absorb the cost",
    "start": 385.051,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "for as long as we could,",
    "start": 386.052,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "and we've even absorbed",
    "start": 387.42,
    "duration": 2.402
  },
  {
    "text": "some of the cost to not pass",
    "start": 389.822,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "it all on to the customer.",
    "start": 391.19,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "But, August 1st,",
    "start": 392.759,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "we did have a 10%",
    "start": 394.193,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "increase in prices,",
    "start": 395.428,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "so we don't have to have",
    "start": 396.763,
    "duration": 1.267
  },
  {
    "text": "another one.",
    "start": 398.03,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "This is brand new analysis",
    "start": 398.965,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "that President Trump",
    "start": 400.333,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "is touting.",
    "start": 401.367,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "It's from the Congressional",
    "start": 401.901,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "Budget Office.",
    "start": 402.802,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "And it projects",
    "start": 403.469,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "that Trump's tariffs over",
    "start": 404.47,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "the course of ten",
    "start": 405.872,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "years are going to reduce,",
    "start": 406.606,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "the federal deficit",
    "start": 408.608,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "by more than $4 trillion",
    "start": 409.475,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "over the next decade,",
    "start": 411.077,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "or about $400 billion, a year.",
    "start": 411.844,
    "duration": 3.203
  },
  {
    "text": "I assume that that",
    "start": 416.249,
    "duration": 2.402
  },
  {
    "text": "your perspective",
    "start": 418.651,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "is that the people",
    "start": 419.452,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "paying for that,",
    "start": 421.287,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "are you and your customers?",
    "start": 424.49,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, it's it's going to be,",
    "start": 429.395,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "the tariff",
    "start": 432.031,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "burden comes on to us,",
    "start": 432.598,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's a matter",
    "start": 434.133,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "of how much of that",
    "start": 435.234,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "we want to pass on",
    "start": 436.002,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "to our customers.",
    "start": 436.969,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "We are,",
    "start": 438.171,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, a",
    "start": 439.405,
    "duration": 0.367
  },
  {
    "text": "relatively small business,",
    "start": 439.772,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "and we already have",
    "start": 441.374,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "the absolute",
    "start": 442.975,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "best of terms",
    "start": 443.643,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "with Fontana Foni.",
    "start": 444.51,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "And there's really",
    "start": 446.846,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "not much to be done",
    "start": 447.78,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "on, on there and either.",
    "start": 448.714,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "So we're",
    "start": 450.349,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "we're forced to raise prices,",
    "start": 451.317,
    "duration": 2.836
  },
  {
    "text": "in order",
    "start": 454.153,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "to keep the quality",
    "start": 454.954,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "and keep the,",
    "start": 457.056,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "the highest level product",
    "start": 458.791,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "we can out there.",
    "start": 460.126,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "If President Trump",
    "start": 461.027,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "were watching right now,",
    "start": 461.894,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "what would you want to say",
    "start": 462.695,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "to him",
    "start": 463.362,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "about the tariffs?",
    "start": 464.864,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, it's just that, sure,",
    "start": 467.066,
    "duration": 2.97
  },
  {
    "text": "we understand the tariffs.",
    "start": 470.036,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "But really",
    "start": 471.27,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "there needs to be transparency.",
    "start": 471.804,
    "duration": 1.869
  },
  {
    "text": "There needs to",
    "start": 473.673,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "be predictability.",
    "start": 474.14,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "The the sudden changes",
    "start": 475.708,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "really disrupt our business.",
    "start": 476.976,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "And if there was just",
    "start": 478.511,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "clear guidance",
    "start": 480.246,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "it would",
    "start": 481.881,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "it would",
    "start": 482.582,
    "duration": 0.333
  },
  {
    "text": "really, really help us out.",
    "start": 482.915,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "And you at home,",
    "start": 484.317,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "if you want",
    "start": 485.351,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "one of these beautiful",
    "start": 486.252,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "pizza ovens",
    "start": 487.587,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "you can shop for Fontana Forni.",
    "start": 488.154,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "That's Forni USA",
    "start": 489.989,
    "duration": 2.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Fontana Forni USA pizza ovens.",
    "start": 492.959,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "You can find them online.",
    "start": 494.927,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Jeremy Lande,",
    "start": 496.095,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "thanks for joining us.",
    "start": 496.662,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Appreciate it.",
    "start": 497.33,
    "duration": 0.433
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, thanks for having me.",
    "start": 499.165,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "Have a good.",
    "start": 500.032,
    "duration": 0.367
  }
]